<DEBUGGING_APPROACH>
When debugging issues:
1. Reproduce the issue consistently
2. Isolate the problem area
3. Form a hypothesis
4. Test the hypothesis
5. Fix and verify
6. Add regression tests
</DEBUGGING_APPROACH>

